      "description": "This vehicle is in truly impeccable, mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from a new car. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches, chips, or dents, and the interior remains in showroom state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly like it just left the dealership floor.",
