      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with a few minor dings and scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery shows typical wear and some light staining, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. While it may not be a showpiece, it has been mechanically maintained to ensure it remains roadworthy and consistent for your daily commute.",
