    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like my own child\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth as silk and perfectly responsive. You won't find another one this pristine in the neighborhood. Come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel of this absolute gem!",
