    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a pinnacle-spec E46 M3, a chassis that defines analog precision. This specimen features a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure absolute torsional rigidity, paired with a VANOS system that has been fully bulletproofed using cryo-treated components for unwavering timing accuracy. The S54 power plant exhibits a razor-sharp throttle response thanks to a recent top-end refresh, including VAC Motorsports rod bearings and high-tensile studs. Handling is dictated by a bespoke, corner-balanced suspension geometry that provides telepathic feedback through the helm. The exterior finish remains deep and lustrous, preserved by a multi-stage ceramic coating. This is an over-engineered marvel, maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
